<section xml:id="numbers-units"  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Reasoning with Units</title>

  <p>
    <ul>
    <li>special characters: &amp;, &gt;, and &lt;</li>
    <li><em>emphasized text</em></li>
    <li><q>quoted text</q></li>
    <li>"hello world"</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
  
  <p>
    Praesent a ligula <em>quis nulla viverra</em> lobortis nec et ligula. Aliquam
